224
00:13:00.923 --> 00:13:02.823
Begitu.

225
00:13:09.723 --> 00:13:13.023
Sepertinya dia berhasil mengambil gambar ketiga pria itu.

226
00:13:13.023 --> 00:13:14.623
Kerja bagus, Conan.

